main event: A citizen in Long Beach, California reported a sighting of a round object with a tail on February 5, 1955.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 14 minutes,The object resembled a flying saucer,The report was confirmed by another witness,Reports varied on the nature of the object including balloon and aircraft possibilities,The observation was a visual type and classified as ground-visual.
sighted object: one round object with a tail
